  "title": "English Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver lessons in an engaging and dynamic manner, based on our curriculum and pedagogy</li>\n  <li>Help students with after school work</li>\n  <li>Assist managers with the daily operation</li>\n  <li>Engage students and help them realize their potential</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Local or prominent university graduate in English teaching field or relevant fields</strong></li>\n  <li>Excellent academic results in primary to secondary English</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate passion in education – committed to nurturing the students and makes effort to continually improve yourself</li>\n  <li>Dynamic and confident, with an approachable disposition</li>\n  <li>Strong communication (both spoken and written) and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Required to work on weekends</li>\n  <li>Candidates with prior teaching experience are preferred</li>\n</ul>",
