    "description": "<p><strong>Smargent Tuition Centre</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Established by a group of dedicated and experienced full time tutors in 2015, Smargent Tuition Center (STC) is one of the rising education providers for tuition and enrichment programmes, ranging from Secondary to Junior College programmes.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Our teachers specialize in Maths, Physics and Chemistry and provide one stop services to the students with our own selectively designed notes and practice questions. We specialize in conducting conventional small group teaching to impart knowledge to our students to the maximum. Through the relentless effort of our tutors, STC has grown rapidly in the past 10 years.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>To date, STC has more than 100 tutors and has nurtured more than 2000 students, many of which have obtained exceptionally good results in various exams and tests.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Currently, Smargent Tuition Center has 4 branches in Singapore, which are located at Bugis, Beauty World, Serangoon and Kovan.</strong></p>",
